import React from 'react';
import { Image, Segment } from 'semantic-ui-react';


const ImageOfRolePlayers = () => {
    return (
        <React.Fragment>
            <Segment style={{ overflow: 'auto', maxHeight: '50vh' }}>
                <Segment.Group horizontal>
                    <Segment> 
                        <Image inline circular src='https://react.semantic-ui.com/images/avatar/small/elliot.jpg' />
                    </Segment>
                    <Segment> 
                        <Image inline circular src='https://react.semantic-ui.com/images/avatar/small/elliot.jpg' />
                    </Segment>
                    <Segment> 
                        <Image inline circular src='https://react.semantic-ui.com/images/avatar/small/elliot.jpg' />
                    </Segment>
                    <Segment> 
                        <Image inline circular src='https://react.semantic-ui.com/images/avatar/small/elliot.jpg' />
                    </Segment>
                    <Segment> 
                        <Image inline circular src='https://react.semantic-ui.com/images/avatar/small/elliot.jpg' />
                    </Segment>
                    <Segment> 
                        <Image inline circular src='https://react.semantic-ui.com/images/avatar/small/elliot.jpg' />
                    </Segment>
                </Segment.Group>
            </Segment>
        </React.Fragment>
    )
}

export default ImageOfRolePlayers;
